info.title: Read web page content
info.description: Pass links/URLs, retrieve cleaned web page content converted to markdown format, processing up to 6 URLs per request.

post.summary: Retrieve cleaned web page content, processing up to 6 URLs per request.

items.description: The raw URL of the web page to fetch. If more than 6 URLs are submitted, only the first 6 will be processed.

urls.description: The raw URL of the web page to fetch. If more than 6 URLs are submitted, only the first 6 will be processed.

200.description: Returns an array of objects each containing the markdown preview URL, src URL, and content of the web page in markdown or an error message if the fetch fails.

preview_url.description: The URL to preview the fetched content in a readable markdown format.

src_url.description: The original URL of the fetched content

content.description: The fetched content in markdown format, content trimmed if its length exceeds 64000.
content.example: Welcome to Jina AI docs or readable error message
